<TEXT>
<P>
ROME, April 23 (Xinhua) -- Italian Prime Minister Romano Prodi
left here today for a 24-hour visit to Kuwait, where he would try
to further his country's relations with the Gulf state.
</P>
<P>
During his visit, Prodi is scheduled to talk with Kuwait's Emir
