The statement also stressed the importance of boosting peace
and stability in the Gulf region.
</P>
<P>
Prodi, who ended a two-day official visit here earlier today,
told the official Kuwait News Agency before departure that "Italy
and Kuwait are increasing day by day their mutual relations, we
must not forget that Italy is now the third commercial partner of
Kuwait."
</P>
<P>
He said he had held discussions with the Kuwaiti officials on
strengthening cooperation in the industrial and military fields.
</P>
<P>
The Italian Prime Minister was accompanied by an official
delegation, including a number of government officials and
businessmen.
</P>
<P>
