built on the very latest technology that not only optimizes
performance and accelerates the population's access to it but also
enables the Internet to be a vehicle for viable electronic
commerce," McNealy said.
</P>
<P>
He also expressed his eagerness to share Sun's knowledge and
experience in this area with China.
</P>
<P>
As an Internet pioneer, Sun technology helped form the backbone
of the explosive growth of the global information network. Sun's
Java, a platform-independent programming environment that was
designed for the Internet and corporate network computing, allows
developers to create applications that can be adapted to any
computer system.
</P>
<P>
With offices in Beijing, Shanghai, Guangzhou, Chengdu and Hong
Kong, Sun's global strategic area is China's inland areas and Hong
Kong. 
