<HEADLINE> Pact Signed to Promote Singapore's Network </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SINGAPORE, April 24 (Xinhua) -- A total of 17 companies and
research organizations signed here today a landmark technology
pact to further develop Singapore One, a Singapore national
multimedia network that will link up every business, home and
school in the country by the year 2000.
</P>
