streaming into Iraq daily across the crossing points on the
borders with Jordan and Turkey.
</P>
<P>
He said that these trucks are loaded with food imported in
accordance with the oil-for-food deal signed by Iraq with the
U.N. last May, Iraqi newspaper Al-Qadissiya reported today.
</P>
