<HEADLINE> Huge Water Project To Seek Int'l Tender For Equipment </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TAIYUAN, April 24 (Xinhua) -- The Wanjiazhai Yellow River
Water-Drawing Project is expected to invite international bidding
for its equipment and machinery soon.
</P>
<P>
Bidding for the civil part of the project opened recently.
</P>
<P>
Items to be purchased include six large pump stations and 44
sets of pump-motor units. Of the total, only five pump stations
and 15 pump-motor units will be open to overseas bidders.
</P>
