infrastructure development and other preparations of the 2000
Olympic Games. He said the coordination commission was studying
some matters that need special attention. Transport is one of
them.
</P>
<P>
Sydney does not have an extensive system of freeway. Even on a
normal day, a highway accident can cause traffic jams for hours.
