were exhibited at the two-week Guangzhou Fair, which opened on
April 15, and businessmen from more than 20 countries and regions
showed an interest in the car.
</P>
<P>
Santanas have sold well and the number in stock is quite small,
sources say, and the company plans to make 230,000 cars this
year. 
