special adviser Honore Ngbanda is expected to arrive here later today
with a message for South African mediators, said an informed source.
</P>
<P>
It was expected that Ngbanda would be carrying Mobutu's reply to
President Nelson Mandela's formal invitation last week for Mobutu to
hold direct talks with rebel leader Laurent Kabila in South Africa
later this week, said the source.
</P>
