talks, the Jordanian Minister said, was the issue of Jordanian
labour force that could meet Malaysia's needs in the various
 02:25CAB078i0423ql02:2702:281445
fields of specialization. He said a Malaysian labour team would be
visiting Jordan for further discussion and to conclude contracts
with the Malaysian side.
</P>
<P>
