<HEADLINE> Sino-Russian Partership Benefits World: Jiang </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, April 23 (Xinhua) -- The establishment and development
of the Sino-Russian strategic coordination partnership is in the
fundamental interests of the two peoples and conducive to world
peace and stability, Chinese President Jiang Zemin said here today.
</P>
<P>
Jiang made the remarks while meeting with Yegor Semeonovich
Stroyev, Chairman of Russian Federation Council this afternoon.
</P>
<P>
He said Sino-Russian friendly relationship is a new type of
state-to-state relationship.
</P>
<P>
In the diversified world today, it is necessary for all
countries to cooperate and seek common development and prosperity
on the basis of equality, mutual benefit and mutual respect, Jiang
said.
</P>
<P>
China will sign an agreement on reduction of military forces in
the border areas with Russia, Kazakhstan, Kyrgyztan and
Tajikistan, which "again demonstrates to the whole world the wish
of our region for peace and development", Jiang said.
</P>
<P>
He added the agreement would have a major impact on the
international community. Stroyev agreed with Jiang, describing the
agreement as a unique document.
</P>
<P>
Recalling his visit to China last year, Stroyev said he was
deeply impressed by China's rapid economic development.
</P>
<P>
He said Russia was studying China's experiences in economic
reforms. It will be mutually beneficial for the two neighboring
countries to expand economic and trade cooperation, he added.
</P>
<P>
During the meeting, Stroyev reiterated Russia's opposition to
NATO's eastward expansion and Jiang expressed China's
understanding about Russia's concern over this issue.
</P>
<P>
"Acts adopted by the NATO should conform with security
interests and wishes of all countries in the region, and should be
conducive to world peace and stability," Jiang said.
</P>
<P>
As for the relations between China's National People's Congress
(NPC) and Russia's parliament, Jiang said that the legislatures of
the two countries have contributed a lot to the development of the
Sino-Russian relations.
</P>
<P>
China's NPC and the Russian parliament have in the past years
increased their contacts, helping promote the understanding and
friendship between the peoples of China and Russia.
</P>
<P>
Jiang expected that the Russian Federation Council, which is
composed of local leaders, to play an important role in enhancing
regional cooperation, he added that China will actively support
such exchanges and cooperation.
</P>
<P>
Agreeing with Jiang, Stroyev said that he was satisfied with
the development of relations between the localities of the two
countries in recent years, and in this regard, both sides should
make further efforts in various fields.
</P>
<P>
During the meeting, Jiang conveyed to Stroyev greetings from
Qiao Shi, Chairman of the Standing Committee of China's National
People's Congress, for which Stroyev expressed his appreciation.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
